@*
    Loads the SLCharts helper (static, dependency-free SVG charts — no Chart.js, no animation).
    Drop this at the top of a page's @@section Scripts { ... } before any SLCharts.* init calls.
    Safe to include on any admin/inventory page (both layouts render the "Scripts" section).
*@
<script src="~/js/sl-charts.v3.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
